parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the airbags not deploying in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light comes on
the airbag system fails to deploy in an accident
the passenger airbag sensor mat is defective
the airbag light stays on after repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cooling fan can cause the vehicle to overheat, leading to engine damage or failure.
symptoms: The cooling fan fails to turn on
the fan motor wiring is melted
the blower motor resistor is faulty

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, leading to accidents.
symptoms: the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the vehicle takes longer to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling can cause the vehicle to lose power and stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
The malfunction of the airbag light can lead to a false sense of security, potentially causing accidents or injuries.
The engine stalling or shutting off can cause accidents, especially when it occurs on a busy highway, and can lead to rear-ending or other collisions.
The failure of the cooling system can cause overheating, engine damage, and potentially lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Anti-freeze leaks through the air vent
boiling sound in the dash board
fuzzy substance growth on the radiator.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of sensors can cause engine stalling, shutting off, or other malfunctions, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The sensor needs to be replaced
often without warning or indication of a problem.
